    {
      "id": "6a42d2170000000000bcb4d0",
      "text": "2026-06-30-05:14:14[おは.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782764055,
      "updated": 1782764065
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43d7650000000000d5441f",
      "text": "2026-06-30-23:49:08 [info.icon] 7月からは通常運転に戻そうと思います",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782830949,
      "updated": 1782831075
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43d7f400000000007e584e",
      "text": "2026-06-30-23:51:32 [info.icon]今は感情を殺して書いています",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782831093,
      "updated": 1782831151
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43d84400000000006cae5a",
      "text": "2026-06-30-23:52:51 [info.icon]やはり、こういうのは良くない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782831172,
      "updated": 1782831211
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43d9790000000000b8aa5e",
      "text": "2026-06-30-23:58:01 [info.icon]何が変わるのかというと、99%は何も変わらん。たまに感情的なことを書く程度。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782831482,
      "updated": 1782831603
